{"tid":2107010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高等法院判決：《國安法》要以符合人權方式詮釋","createTime":"2020-07-13T14:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T15:45:17.000Z","uid":101392,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"37e9d9c41a0e694da5c3925a45a7eeebff2e73a3","tid":2107010,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"「7.  無論如何,假若香港的司法機關在處理一宗實質的案件時，必須考慮到港區國安法與基本法的規定是否一致，基於：<br />\n<br />\n(1) 普通法的一貫原則；<br />\n<br />\n(2) 香港的司法機關需要保障基本法第三章賦予香港居民的基本權利的憲制責任，及<br />\n<br />\n(3) 港區國安法第四條定明：「香港特別行政區維護國家安全應當尊重和保障人權，依法保護香港特別行政區居民根據香港特別行政區基本法和《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》、《經濟、社會與文化權利的國際公約》適用於香港的有關規定享有的包括言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由在內的權利和自由」，<br />\n<br />\n香港的司法機關也應該盡可能在合乎法律原則及合理的情況下，給予港區國安法及基本法第三章賦予香港居民的基本權利的相關規定作出一致的詮釋。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=129354&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D129354%26currpage%3DT&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=d3a7f13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=129354&amp;currpage=T</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 《郭卓堅訴香港特別行政區首長林鄭月娥女士》 [2020] HKCFI 1520第7段"},{"pid":"b9ff74bc5e62b04def7169faa19caafc12c7a8eb","tid":2107010,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxxDjgm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxxDjgm.png&h=b6885a73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b6f35e70551d7ee676acb479a6d98df3fda9549","tid":2107010,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:00:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2819dfdca95dc7c2c27ac00dcdf1f7fb7cd494ec","tid":2107010,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b6f35e70551d7ee676acb479a6d98df3fda9549","tid":2107010,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2